2006-08-11  Sjoerd Simons <sjoerd@luon.net>

	* src/rbgtkuimanager.c: Add G_CHILD_ADD and G_CHILD_REMOVE to respectively
	Gtk::UIManager#insert_action_group and Gtk::UIManager#remove_action_group.
	Without these the action_group can be garbage collected while it can still
	be used for callbacks (which causes a nice segv).

2006-08-09  Sjoerd Simons <sjoerd@luon.net>

	* src/rbgtkscrolledwindow.c: Added G_CHILD_ADD to
	Gtk::ScrolledWindow#add_with_viewport

