	Gtk::MenuItem#set_submenu and Gtk::MenuItem#remove_menu.

2006-05-08  Masao Mutoh  <mutoh@highway.ne.jp>

	* src/rbgtkdialog.c: Added Gtk::Dialog#get_response as an alias of 
	Gtk::Dialog#get_response_for_widget. 
	* src/rbgtkcurve.c: Added Gtk::Curve#gamma=. 
	* src/rbgtkclipboard.c: Gtk::Clipboard#set_can_store accept nil as an
	argument.
	* src/rbgtkwindow.c: Gtk::Window#active_(focus|default) was wrong name.
	So they've been deprecated and added 
	Gtk::Window#activate_(focus|default) instead.

