	* sample/misc/fileselection.rb, itemfactory.rb, itemfactory2.rb: 
	Show "Deprecated" message first.
	* sample/misc/cairo-pong.rb: Fixed warning when calling 
	@drawing_area.queue_draw after @drawing_area is broken.

