	rbgtkfontbutton.c, rbgtkfilechooserwidget.c, rbgtkaction.c, rbgtktoggleaction.c,
	rbgtkradioaction.c: Added for GTK+-2.4.
	* src/rbgtkoptionmenu.c, rbgtkcombo.c: Deprecated(GTK_DISABLE_DEPRECATED).

