	* src/gtk2.def: Add gdk_windowattr_get_type.
	* src/rbgdkkeyval.c: Add Gdk::Keyval.convert_case. 
	* src/rbgdkwindowattr.c: Added. 
	* src/rbgtknotebook.c: Add Gtk::Notebook#n_pages.
	Gtk::Notebook#page= works with negative value.

2003-10-06  Masao Mutoh  <mutoh@highway.ne.jp>

	* src/rbgdkspan.c: Removed. Use [x, y, width] instead.
	* src/rbgtk.h: Revmoe GDK_TYPE_SPAN.
	* src/rbgdkregion.c: Remove Gdk::Region#eql?, #&, #-, #|.
	Merge Gdk::Region#union_with_rect and #union.
	Gdk::Region#offset, #shrink returns self.
	Fix segfault for Gdk::Region#rectangles.
	Gdk::Region#spans_intersect_each() accept [x, y, width] not Gdk::Span.

