	#set_column_spacing, #column_spacing=, #column_spacing #default_col_spacing to 
	Gtk::Table#set_row_spacings, #row_spacings=, #row_spacings, #set_column_spacings, 
	#column_spacings=, #column_spacings, default_column_spacing
	Add Gtk::Tabel#set_row_spacing(row), #set_column_spacing(col).
	* src/rbgtkprogressbar.c: Remove methods for deprecated properties.
	* src/rbgtkcontainer.c: Add Gtk::Container.child_property, .child_properties, 
	Gtk::Container#child_type, Gtk::Container#child_get_property, 
	Gtk::Container#child_set_property.
	* src/rbgtkcontainer.c, rbgtk.h: Add rbgtkcontainer_register_child_property_setter/getter.

2003-04-26  Masao Mutoh  <mutoh@highway.ne.jp>

	* src/rbgtkobject.c: Remove Gtk::Object#user_data, #user_data=, #set_user_data. 

